                        <li><strong>Nurse Practitioners (NOC 31302):</strong> priority within Health Authority stream.</li>
                        <li><strong>Allied Health (NOC 31201, 31203, 32109, 32101, 32104):</strong> physiotherapists, occupational therapists, medical lab technologists, paramedics.</li>
                        <li><strong>Early Childhood Educators (NOC 42202):</strong> dedicated childcare educator pathway with reduced SIRS requirements.</li>
                        <li><strong>Construction Tradespeople (NOC 72100-72500 series):</strong> carpenters, electricians, plumbers, heavy equipment operators.</li>
                        <li><strong>Tech 35 NOC list:</strong> all designated technology occupations including software, engineering, and cybersecurity.</li>
